{"tid":658492,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【Google I/O 2018】Android P 發表、Google 服務全面升級","createTime":"2018-05-09T04:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T16:56:22.000Z","uid":34178,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"156f5ad1f6d8f877ee2d32c86788fd4acb61d1fb","tid":658492,"uid":34178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"文：Tony<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2018/05/180509_androidgoogle_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2018%2F05%2F180509_androidgoogle_01.jpg&h=c9135f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n智能裝置系統 Android 誕生已有十週年，當中加入不少 Google 服務如 Google Assistant、Google Map、Google Lens、Google Photo 等都提升了用家的體驗。在今年 Google I/O 2018 開發者大會，Google 宣佈 Android P 系統及將 Google 服務作全面升級。<br />\n<br />\nAndroid P 加入全新操作方式，AI 功能令手機更省電<br />\n近年流行全面屏手機，為此 Google 亦為 Android P 加入全新的操作方式，估計亦為將來推出的全面屏手機作好準備。新的操作方式已不需依靠屏幕底下的按鍵操作，透過手勢及屏幕底部的小小長條，已可進行日常操作及切換 Apps，或許大家會認為操作上有點模仿 iOS，但方便用家於全面屏單手操作，就是好的操作方式，相信 Android 用家亦不會介意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2018/05/180509_androidgoogle_02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2018%2F05%2F180509_androidgoogle_02.jpg&h=479c58cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為手機系統加入 Machine learning 的 AI 人工智能功能，已不是新鮮事，今次 Google P 主要應用在省電及使用安全的範疇。<br />\n<br />\nAndroid P 將會加入 Adaptive Battery 及 Adaptive Brightness 功能，透過學習用家的使用習慣，從而調整 CPU 時頻及屏幕亮度，從而令手機更省電。今次於系統內更加入 Dashboard、App Timer 及 Wind Down 功能，可以讓知道或設計使用 Apps 的時間。當中的 Wind Down 功能，更會於環境全黑的環境啟動，並將屏幕轉為黑白色，減少大家於全黑環境閱讀時，屏幕藍光對眼睛的傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2018/05/180509_androidgoogle_03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2018%2F05%2F180509_androidgoogle_03.jpg&h=8b365852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn01.dcfever.com/articles/news/2018/05/180509_androidgoogle_04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn01.dcfever.com%2Farticles%2Fnews%2F2018%2F05%2F180509_androidgoogle_04.jpg&h=81f3514b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10989a7c12a36a79d69afd79824f6105e67d04e9","tid":658492,"uid":34178,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"年年都話慳電 都係唔信最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0678ccde6c57b55cd81bc527c2179cee78af449","tid":658492,"uid":101900,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"反而對佢個全屏手勢有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413d5a50e36530ac31cc05e360b3b892fd469601","tid":658492,"uid":34178,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b0678ccde6c57b55cd81bc527c2179cee78af449","tid":658492,"uid":101900,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"反而對佢個全屏手勢有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"算唔算抄IOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9459f57cadb04077a0ec0b4ff30915c408bc4478","tid":658492,"uid":79355,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"413d5a50e36530ac31cc05e360b3b892fd469601","tid":658492,"uid":34178,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b0678ccde6c57b55cd81bc527c2179cee78af449","tid":658492,"uid":101900,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:05:56.000Z","msg":"反而對佢個全屏手勢有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:14:27.000Z","msg":"算唔算抄IOS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T05:19:04.000Z","msg":"擺明抄"},{"pid":"5df07ed55ae5b4d46a72e8871697b7cd393cfac4","tid":658492,"uid":68094,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018